


***************************	Useful fields && Notes ***********************


plan.key = The plan without its latest build number.  eg. ITSI-ITGT.

projectName = Just the main project name.  eg. ITSI, APPSC etc.

number = latest build number. (This is what we care about in most KPI's.) eg.
223

The following two categories are useful in subdividing the results:

1. Tests + Build or Only Build
# Useful for separating out testless builds from the ones with tests.
isTestlessBuild="false" or "true"


2. Main branch OR feature branches
# The main branch of a plan is "chain", and various feature branches would be
# in "chain_branch". 

plan.type = "chain" or "chain_branch"

# Also, note: they have slightly different names.  plan.type = chain, name eg.
# ITSI-ITGT plan.type = chain_type  eg. ITSI-ITGT255


