3. Get the Mean success rate of all builds of the release plans:

Q: Do you want to consider only the latest builds of each plan or combine them all?

  index="bamboo" AND sourcetype="Bamboo Input" AND plan.type="chain" AND isTestlessBuild="true" earliest=1 AND latest=now
| dedup buildResultKey | eval total_build=1, success = if(buildState == "Successful", 1, 0), successful_build_rate = round ((success/total_build)*100, 2)

Only latest plans: 

--> add | sort -number | dedup plan.key in the search.

index="bamboo" AND sourcetype="Bamboo Input" AND plan.type="chain" AND isTestlessBuild="true" earliest=1 AND latest=now
| dedup buildResultKey | sort -number | dedup plan.key  | eval total_build=1, success = if(buildState == "Successful", 1, 0), successful_build_rate = round ((success/total_build)*100, 2)



